TextBody:
Hello Alex,

I'm just following up on this ticket. We split off the more pressing "FSAC reports from UK servers returning outdated information" issue to its own ticket, so this ticket is just for the issues with the Inda and Phoenix servers. You indicated that you wanted to put this ticket on the backburner, but I wasn't sure if you wanted to archive it and reopen it at a later date.

That last steps we took were to provide your NetApp team the documentation on the account requirements. We are trying to resolve the Error, "Failed to connect to \INF-FS02.IN.AEXP.COMIPC$: This user isn't allowed to sign in to this computer".

Please let me know how you'd like to proceed.

Thank you,

Joshua Sexton
